<body>
    <p>Take a number from a user and write a  function which checks wheather the number is even or odd. Assign the result to a variable and log that in the variable in the console.</p>

    <script>

        let num = prompt("Enter a number");

        function even_odd(num)
        {
            if(num%2==0)
            {
                console.log("The number is even");
            }
            else
            {
                console.log("The number is odd");
            }
        }

        even_odd(num);
        

    </script>


